  "body": "\r\nThe current implementation of tags component needs to be wrapped in a scroll-view for the user to be able to scroll an horizontal list of tags. However the designs as is in the figma link show that tags components fades out which currently is not implemented. \r\n\r\nfigma: https://www.figma.com/file/h9wo4GipgZURbqqr1vShFN/Communities-for-Mobile?node-id=5488%3A224643\r\n\r\nWe dont want to do away with the current implementation. What we want is to address the case where tags are scrollable and have the fading effect\r\n\r\n",
